21. It was cruel Advice that the Cardinal gave to the Emperour; 
                     Ʋtere jure tuo Caeſar, Sectumque Lutheri, Enſe, rotâ, ponto, funibus, igne, neca: Ariſe Caeſar, take thy Authority, and deſtroy Luthers Sect by the Sword, upon

the Wheel, in the Sea, with Ropes and Fire.

